---
import ButtonLiveProduction from "../../../components/ButtonLiveProduction/ButtonLiveProduction.astro";
import IconNatatoko from "../Natanya/IconNatatoko.astro";
import ProjectSlider from "../ProjectSlider.astro";
---

<article class="max-w-[1244px] mx-auto z-10 relative py-20 sm:rounded-3xl overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Outnament Lines (Top) -->
  <img
    src="/images/project-ournament-lines.png"
    width="1000"
    height="1000"
    loading="lazy"
    alt=""
    class="absolute pointer-events-none z-0 left-0 top-0 min-w-[600px] sm:min-w-[1000px]"
  />

  <!-- Outnament Lines (Bottom) -->
  <img
    src="/images/project-ournament-lines-btm-red.png"
    loading="lazy"
    width="1000"
    height="1000"
    alt=""
    class="absolute pointer-events-none z-0 right-0 bottom-0 min-w-[500px] sm:min-w-[1000px]"
  />

  <div class="lg:px-16 sm:px-10 px-5 relative z-10">
    <h3 class="sr-only">Natatoko</h3>

    <IconNatatoko />

    <h4 class="sr-only">About Natatoko</h4>

    <p class="sm:text-2xl text-lg !leading-150 text-dark mt-10">
      <strong class="font-semibold">Build a customizable well designed web store in 5 minutes</strong> with ease and sell
      products that supported by comprehensive income estimation and web traffic analytics for our users
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="portfolio-images py-10 sm:py-20">
    <ProjectSlider />
  </div>

  <div class="lg:px-16 sm:px-10 px-5 relative z-10">
    <p class="sm:text-2xl text-lg !leading-150 text-dark">
      It offers <strong>comprehensive income estimation and web traffic analytics</strong> to help users make informed business
      decisions. Setup, orders, products and business analysis are all easily adjustable with Natatoko.
      <br />
      <br />
      We also allows users to <strong>conveniently and effortlessly customize the visual appeal</strong> of their ecommerce
      platform to reflect their company's brand.
      <br />
      <br />
      Natatoko <strong>makes sure the store can be up and running in a matter of minutes.</strong>
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 sm:mt-[4.4rem] mb-10 sm:mb-14">
      <ButtonLiveProduction name="natatoko.com" link="https://natatoko.com" />
    </div>

    <div class="pl-5 sm:pl-8 flex items-start space-x-4 sm:space-x-10">
      <a href="#" class="tracking-tight font-semibold leading-6">
        <span class="block text-xl sm:text-[32px] text-dark leading-4 sm:!leading-100">nataicons</span>
        <span class="inline-flex text-sm sm:text-xl space-x-[6px] text-slate-700 sm:pt-2">
          <span>a</span>
          <span
            ><svg class="w-[18px] sm:w-6 sm:h-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <g clip-path="url(#clip0_67_250)">
                <path
